DEVNOTes


--- Physics

- Category bitmasks
Dude            0x1
PinkRocks       0x10
FireBall        0x100
Alien           0x1000
BlackHole       0x10000
Dragon          0x100000

- Collision bitmask (how things react to gravity)
Dude            0x0         (no one)
PinkRocks       0x101011    (dude,pinkrock,alien,dragon)
FireBall        0x0         (no one)
Alien           0x0         (no one)
BlackHole       0x0         (no one)
Dragon          0x0         (no one)

- Contact bitmask
Dude            0x111110    (everone but dude)
PinkRocks       0x1         (only dude)
FireBall        0x1         (only dude)
Alien           0x1         (only dude)
BlackHole       0x1         (only dude)
Dragon          0x1         (only dude)



